		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I wonder why a game as simple as Metroid even needs the 8KB of WRAM... Of course I never actually played the game, so I might be missing something obvious, but my first impression is that the developers were just too lazy to engineer the program for 2KB of RAM.
